        <div id="executive-summary" class="executive-summary">
            <h2>🎯 Executive Summary</h2>
            
            <p><strong>Business Challenge:</strong> Organizations need intelligent automation that processes customer communications, validates business requirements against ERP systems, and controls when AI assistants like Microsoft Copilot can create sales orders.</p>
            
            <p><strong>Proposed Solution:</strong> An AI-powered middleware solution that intercepts customer emails, extracts order details using advanced NLP, validates information against Business Central/ERP systems, orchestrates multi-level approval workflows, and provides granular control over Copilot's sales order creation capabilities.</p>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 20px;">
