                    <h4>✅ Smart Approvals</h4>
                    <p>Configurable multi-level workflows with timeout handling</p>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align: center;">
                    <h4>🛡️ Copilot Control</h4>
                    <p>Prevents unauthorized order creation while enabling automation</p>
